## Expected behavior
I expect memory use to go up the first time I run this. Then maybe a little more on the next couple of runs and then level off. Perhaps eventually fall again.

## Actual behavior
Memory goes from 72MB before running this code to 158MB after. On the second run, it goes up to 169MB, on the third run, 180MB. Next run, 194MB, then 213MB, then 233MB, then 252MB, 271MB, 290MB, etc... Here's a diff of the memory snapshot between the first run and after several runs. 
